---
title: Spiced Beef Fajita Bowls with charred veg and lime rice
description: A tortilla-less take on this Tex-Mex favourite. These fajita bowls feature zesty lime rice, spiced roasted veg, a refreshing creamy sauce and juicy beef rump cooked exactly how you like it.
